        <tr><td>Pilot tube repair or replacement</td><td>$180 to $280</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Gas valve replacement (magnetic latch wear)</td><td>$480 to $680</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Gas pressure / manifold rebalance (plumber referral)</td><td>$200 to $600</td></tr>
